pageContext.claim: “Peggy Noonan, the simplistic writer for Trump Haters all, is stuck in the past glory of Reagan and has no idea what is happening with the Radical Left Democrats, or how vicious and desperate they are. Mueller had to correct his ridiculous statement, Peggy never understood it!”
pageContext.analysis: Peggy Noonan aside, special counsel Robert Mueller did not correct his May 29 statement or any element of his report.
